My LiveJournal Trick-or-Treat Haul
darrkflame goes trick-or-treating, dressed up as Soda Can.
paintingwalden gives you 15 light orange coffee-flavoured nuggets.
shesgoneagain tricks you! You lose 5 pieces of candy!
thegreatconnito gives you 17 green licorice-flavoured pieces of chewing gum.
darrkflame ends up with 27 pieces of candy.
Go trick-or-treating! Username:
